### About the Project
Gullet Stuffer is a competitive eating competition and charity fundraiser held annually in Seattle, WA. Eaters compete side by side in a 10 minute frenzy for a chance to claim the crown.

All profits from the event each year goes towards [Seattle Community Fridge](https://www.instagram.com/seattlecommunityfridge/?hl=en), an amazing mutual aid group that hosts refrigerators throughout Seattle that are available to anyone that needs them.

Our instagram page [@gulletstuffer](https://www.instagram.com/gulletstuffer/?hl=en) is the best place to get the latest updates, and videos from all our past events can be found on [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/@MaxwellCromsBrillz/videos).
